Build-Depends: dh-python, python3-setuptools, python3-all, debhelper (>= 9)
Standards-Version: 3.9.6
Homepage: http://tvlinker.ozmartians.com

Package: tvlinker
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, python3-pyqt5, python3-bs4, python3-lxml
Description: TV show link scraper + downloader for tv-release.net with a modern PyQt5 GUI
 PyQt5 based desktop widget for scraping and organising links from various download feeds/sites. 
 .
 Currently supporting tv-release.net link scraping together with integration with real-debrid link
 unrestrictor (debrid) service via their API (NOTE: a valid real-debrid account and api_token is
 necessary for this to work).
 .
 Integrates with a number of download managers; Aria2 RPC Daemon (windows/linux),
 pyload (windows/linux), IDM (Internet Download Manager; windows only). A built-in download
 accelerator is also available and is the default setting.
 .
